text: Patuakhali Sadar () is an upazila of Patuakhali District in the Division of Barisal, Bangladesh. ==Geography== Patuakhali Sadar is located at . It has 55,194 households and a total area of 362.62 km2. ==Related pages== *Upazilas of Bangladesh *Districts of Bangladesh *Divisions of Bangladesh ==References== Category:Upazilas of Patuakhali District
title: Patuakhali Sadar Upazila
